{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_123","type":"agent_message","text":"The `jar` protocol issue is clearly a native-image build-arg problem; the repo already handles the same thing for `kotlin-scripting-jvm` in its test `build.gradle`. The `JvmScriptingHostConfigurationKt` failure looks like a runtime class-initialization issue around `System.getProperty(\"java.home\")`, so I’m checking whether this library already has per-test native-image args and whether the fix should be build-time init, not more reflection metadata."}}
